    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Would the hon. Member say that the better-off people should borrow money at 4 per cent. instead of being loaned it at 3¼? I want to be clear what the hon. Member is talking about.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
