                Mr. Hare
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-011dd133-3505-4177-936d-e932e597c3b8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-05-30/debates/dc1f6775-f37b-456c-9aba-7ca84739f564/Title#contribution-011dd133-3505-4177-936d-e932e597c3b8">
